    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen boasts a flawless power curve facilitated by its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS system, delivering 333hp through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by a limited-slip differential and an unblemished undercarriage. Finished in a deep luster with zero bolster wear, this E46 represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically synchronized masterpiece with optimal compression and zero deferred maintenance.",
