    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2021 Executive Sport SUV is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously maintained to satisfy even the most demanding collector. The exterior is finished in a deep Metallic Obsidian that has been preserved with a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring a mirror-like finish free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium Nappa leather retains its original matte finish with no signs of wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct 'new car' scent. This vehicle has been exclusively garage-kept and has never seen a car wash brush or a drop of rain whenever possible. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a full, documented service history from the local dealership and a recently completed 150-point inspection. With zero curb rash on the 21-inch alloy wheels and a spotless undercarriage, this car is the closest you can get to buying brand new. It comes complete with both keys, all original manuals, and custom-fit all-weather floor mats.",
      "price": 48500.0,
